description: Product of unitary divisors of n.
comments: Also appears to be smallest number m such that A066296[m]=n.
links: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n=1,...,1000
prog: (PARI) { for (n=1, 1000, s=divisors(n); a=1; for (i=2, length(s), d=s[i]; if (gcd(d, n/d)==1, a*=d)); write("b061537.txt", n, " ", a) ) } [From _Harry J. Smith_, Jul 24 2009]
author: _Labos Elemer_, May 15 2001
extensions: Corrected and edited by _Jaroslav Krizek_, Mar 05 2009
